&lt;li&gt;Partner with Procurement on purchase order and vendor onboarding issues&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Collaborate with Accounting, Tax, and other finance teams on cross-functional projects&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Support the AP Manager with special projects and ad-hoc analysis&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
