&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Experience with AP automation&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Advanced Excel skills (pivot tables, VLOOKUPs, complex formulas)&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Knowledge of SOX compliance requirements and audit procedures&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Accounting background&lt;/li&gt;
